<h1>{{title}}</h1>
<p>{{subtitle}}</p>

<h2>Strong points:</h2>
<ol>
{{#each features}}
    <li>{{feat}}</li>
{{/each}}
</ol>

<h2>Quotes:</h2>
{{{quotes}}}

<h2>Helpers</h2>
<h4>Make Link</h4>
<p>
    Helpers are functions to help. {{makeLink "Read More" "http://handlebarsjs.com/block_helpers.html"}}
</p>
<h4>Text Component</h4>
<p>
    You can for example create {{dangerText "Alert Text!"}}
</p>
<h4>Helpers with Options</h4>
<p>
    {{transformText "You can send options to your helpers" transformation="cap"}}
</p>
<h4>Global Options</h4>
<p>
    {{globalOptions}}
</p>

<h2>Block Helpers</h2>
{{#makeRadio "size"}}
    Small
    Medium
    Large
{{/makeRadio}}

<p>Or you can execute different blocks like this</p>
<p>Are 1 and 2 equal?</p>
{{#ifeq 2 "2" }}
{{successText "Numbers are equal"}}
{{else}}
{{dangerText "Numbers not equal"}}
{{/ifeq}}

<p>Another example with block helpers</p>
{{#if sunnyDay}}
<blockquote class="imgur-embed-pub" lang="en" data-id="a/5AryP"><a href="//imgur.com/5AryP">When the sun is directly overhead in Hawaii, it looks like a bad video game render</a></blockquote><script async src="//s.imgur.com/min/embed.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
{{else}}
<blockquote class="imgur-embed-pub" lang="en" data-id="mVbmFQp"><a href="//imgur.com/mVbmFQp">Cloud pouring Rain.... Captured from flight</a></blockquote><script async src="//s.imgur.com/min/embed.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
{{/if}}
